snippet.title: Amber Heard Responds To Being Fired From Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
►Amber Heard Responds To Being Fired From Aquaman 2
The majority of people believe that Zack Snyder's Justice League exists solely to boost HBO Max subscriptions. Despite the fact that 70 million dollars for a remake of a failed film may appear to be a large sum, Netflix and Disney have routinely spent more on unique content. Indeed, if Warner Bros. had been sold on Snyder's initial concept, Joss Whedon would not have had to reshoot 95% of the film after Snyder had left.
